Home / News / Regional Planning & Transit / Minneapolis setting vision for Snelling Yards site The Snelling Yards site is a block north of the 46th Street Station on the Blue Line light rail transit route in Minneapolis. (Staff photo: Bill Klotz) Minneapolis setting vision for Snelling Yards site By: Cali Owings August 6, 2015 4:16 pm 0 The site has been in the cityâ€™s vision for transit-oriented development for years, but ownership issues got in the way.
